        <abstract>
            <p>In consideration of CD’s health, withdraws his request for notes on GHL’s articles.</p> 
<p>While in Freiburg, heard that August Weismann’s inaugural address on CD’s views [<hi rend="italic">Über die Berechtigung der Darwin’schen Theorie</hi> (1868)] created a sensation.</p> 
